                    <span>I bought this dvd thinking that I wanted to see homes that Frank Lloyd Wright built, but this dvd does that no justice.  This is a documentary of Frank Lloyd Wrights life, not a movie about his work.  I do not suggest buying this unless you want to know about the man, not his work.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The Making of a great house</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
